# Story 049: per-run staker snapshot artifacts. Regenerate via
# `npm run snapshot:phlimbo-v1` immediately before broadcasting
# `migrate-phlimbo-v1-to-v2`. They are environment- and timing-sensitive
# and should not be checked in.
